20
00:01:49,780 --> 00:01:53,859
Blogger moved to Google’s campus but Ev
didn’t enjoy it and soon sold all of his

21
00:01:53,859 --> 00:02:00,120
Google stock and left the company. He financed
Noah’s audio blogging project, which allowed

22
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:05,500
voice based blogs recorded from a phone, in
