asked him to be the CEO. Ev wanted an active
role himself but was also involved in other

73
00:06:21,139 --> 00:06:27,670
projects. Jack accepted the role.
In June 2007, Twitter had grown to almost

74
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:33,949
